data.name: $FILE_ID
data.comment: {locked} This is the file ID for this localization file. This string value should not be used or translated.

data.name: Save
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] The title of save button on property pane.

data.name: Close
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] The accessible label of button for closing property pane.

data.name: SaveConfirmation
data.value: We saved your changes in the property pane.
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Confirmation message for the screen reader.

data.name: PropertyPaneBackPage
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] The title of the back button on the property pane.

data.name: PropertyPaneNextPage
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] The title of the next button on the property pane.

data.name: PropertyPanePageOfPages
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Placeholder={0} is current page number, placeholder={1} is total pages.

data.name: PropertyPaneTitle
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Append settings to title for the screen reader, {0} is placeholder for webpart title.

data.name: PropertyPaneAriaLabel
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Aria label for the pane

data.name: UpdatedPropertyPaneAriaLabel
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Aria label for the pane, {0} is the title of the property pane.

data.name: PropertyPaneEmptyStateDescription
data.value: No settings to change for this web part.
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Property Pane empty configuration message.

data.name: PropertyPaneDeletionStateDescription
data.value: No settings available. The web part or dashboard card using this property pane was deleted.
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Property Pane empty configuration message.

data.name: PropertyPaneFetchingSettingsDataLabel
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Property Pane fetching settings data label.

data.name: NoOpOnRefreshPropertyPaneText
data.value: refreshPropertyPane is a No Op, because the property pane is currently not attached to the web part {0}.
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]Log when it is a no op on refreshPropertyPane. {0} is the web part instance id, which invoked refreshPropertyPane.

data.name: ApplyButtonAriaDescription
data.value: Changes made on the property pane will be applied to the web part.
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]VSO:684173 - Changes made on the property pane will be applied to the web part.

data.name: ToggleOnText
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Label text of toggle control when the toggle is on.

data.name: ToggleOffText
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Label text of toggle control when the toggle is off.

data.name: NoDynamicDataReturnedErrorText
data.value: Entered dynamic resource path does not return any dynamic data.
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]VSO:684173 - Error message for when the entered dynamic resource path does not return any valid data.

data.name: ConnectToDynamicDataSource
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]String displayed on the button to connect to a dynamic data source.

data.name: ConnectToDynamicDataSourceDescription
data.value: Click to connect to a dynamic data source.
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]VSO:684173 - Description for screen readers for the connect to source button.

data.name: DynamicDataSourcesDropdownLabel
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]Label for the dynamic data source dropdown on the DynamicDataWidget.

data.name: DynamicDataPropertiesDropdownLabel
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]Label for the properties dropdown on the DynamicDataWidget. {0} is the selected source.

data.name: DynamicDataRemoveConnectionText
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]Text for the remove connection button.

data.name: InvalidPropertyValueDepthWarning
data.value: Value for {0} is invalid. Possible values are {1} through {2}.
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]VSO:684173 - Warning text when an invlaid value is sent for maxPropertyValueDepth. {0} name of the property, {1} and {2} are the supported boundaries.

data.name: DynamicDataSecondaryGroupButtonLabel
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Label text of button to bring up secondary group in the property pane.

data.name: DynamicDataSecondaryGroupIconButtonLabel
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-WebPartInfra] Label text of more icon button to bring up secondary group in the property pane.

data.name: NoDataSourceErrorMessage
data.value: No source available. Add a web part to your page that has the ability to connect.
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]Error message displayed under dropdown when no data source available.

data.name: LearnMoreLabel
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]Label text of learn more link.

data.name: AltText
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-ImageWebpart]Text to display for the alternate text textbox

data.name: AltTextDesc
data.value: Alternative text is for people who are blind or have low vision. Briefly describe how this image is relevant to the page.
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-ImageWebpart]Text to display as the description for the altText control in prop pane

data.name: AccessibilityTitle
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-ImageWebpart]Text to display for the alternate text textbox

data.name: AccessibilityDesc
data.value: Provide alternative text to describe this image to people who are blind or low vision.
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-ImageWebpart]Text to display as the description for the altText control in prop pane

data.name: WebAIMLink
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-ImageWebpart]Text to display for the web aim link in order to help user to understand altText

data.name: MarkImageAsDecorative
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-ImageWebpart]Text to display for the mark image as decorative switch

data.name: DecorativeTooltipDesc
data.value: This lets people using screen readers know that the image doesn't add information to the page and doesn't need alt text. Example: Stylistic borders
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-ImageWebpart]Text to display on the mark as decorative tooltip

data.name: OnAriaLabel
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-ImageWebpart]The aria label for accessibility when mark as decorative toggle is on.

data.name: OffAriaLabel
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-ImageWebpart]The aria label for accessibility when mark as decorative toggle is off.

data.name: IconAriaLabel
data.comment: [Tag:ODSP-WEX-ImageWebpart]The aria label for the info icon of the mark as decorative toggle.
